WITH RNK AS ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, EVENT_DATE, RANK() OVER(PARTITION BY PLAYER_ID ORDER BY EVENT_DATE) AS NUM FROM ACTIVITY ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, EVENT_DATE AS FIRST_LOGIN FROM RNK WHERE NUM = 1
SELECT DISTINCT PLAYER_ID AS PLAYER_ID, MIN(EVENT_DATE) AS FIRST_LOGIN FROM ACTIVITY GROUP BY PLAYER_ID
SELECT T.PLAYER_ID, MIN(T.EVENT_DATE) AS FIRST_LOGIN FROM ACTIVITY T GROUP BY T.PLAYER_ID
SELECT PLAYER_ID, MIN(EVENT_DATE) AS FIRST_LOGIN FROM ACTIVITY WHERE GAMES_PLAYED IS NOT NULL GROUP BY PLAYER_ID
SELECT PLAYER_ID,EVENT_DATE AS FIRST_LOGIN FROM (SELECT DISTINCT PLAYER_ID, EVENT_DATE, DENSE_RANK() OVER( PARTITION BY PLAYER_ID ORDER BY EVENT_DATE ASC) AS RANK_ FROM ACTIVITY) O WHERE O.RANK_ = 1
SELECT PLAYER_ID, FIRST_LOGIN FROM ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, EVENT_DATE FIRST_LOGIN, DENSE_RANK() OVER( PARTITION BY PLAYER_ID ORDER BY EVENT_DATE ) POZ FROM ACTIVITY ) SRC WHERE POZ = 1
SELECT DISTINCT(PLAYER_ID), MIN(EVENT_DATE) AS FIRST_LOGIN FROM ACTIVITY GROUP BY PLAYER_ID ORDER BY EVENT_DATE
SELECT PLAYER_ID, EVENT_DATE AS FIRST_LOGIN FROM ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, EVENT_DATE, DENSE_RANK() OVER(PARTITION BY PLAYER_ID ORDER BY EVENT_DATE ) RNK FROM ACTIVITY) A WHERE RNK = 1 ORDER BY 1
WITH R AS ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, EVENT_DATE, RANK() OVER(PARTITION BY PLAYER_ID ORDER BY EVENT_DATE) AS PLAYER_RANK FROM ACTIVITY ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, EVENT_DATE AS FIRST_LOGIN FROM R WHERE PLAYER_RANK=1
SELECT PLAYER_ID, EVENT_DATE AS FIRST_LOGIN FROM (SELECT PLAYER_ID, EVENT_DATE, ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY PLAYER_ID ORDER BY EVENT_DATE) AS RN FROM ACTIVITY) A WHERE RN = 1
SELECT PLAYER_ID, EVENT_DATE AS FIRST_LOGIN FROM ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, EVENT_DATE, DENSE_RANK () OVER (PARTITION BY PLAYER_ID ORDER BY EVENT_DATE)RNK FROM ACTIVITY )B WHERE B.RNK=1
SELECT PLAYER_ID, EVENT_DATE AS FIRST_LOGIN FROM(SELECT PLAYER_ID,EVENT_DATE,ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY PLAYER_ID ORDER BY EVENT_DATE) AS RANK FROM ACTIVITY) A WHERE A.RANK = 1
SELECT PLAYER_ID AS PLAYER_ID , MIN(EVENT_DATE) AS FIRST_LOGIN FROM ACTIVITY GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, FIRST_LOGIN FROM ( SELECT T1.PLAYER_ID, T1.EVENT_DATE AS FIRST_LOGIN, ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY PLAYER_ID ORDER BY EVENT_DATE) AS ROW_NUM FROM ACTIVITY T1 ) T2 WHERE T2.ROW_NUM = 1

WITH EXAMPLE AS( SELECT PLAYER_ID, EVENT_DATE, ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY PLAYER_ID ORDER BY EVENT_DATE) AS RANKI FROM ACTIVITY) SELECT PLAYER_ID, EVENT_DATE AS FIRST_LOGIN FROM EXAMPLE WHERE RANKI = 1
WITH CTE AS (SELECT PLAYER_ID,EVENT_DATE AS FIRST_LOGIN, ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY PLAYER_ID ORDER BY EVENT_DATE) AS LOGIN FROM ACTIVITY) SELECT PLAYER_ID,FIRST_LOGIN FROM CTE WHERE LOGIN=1
SELECT A.PLAYER_ID,A.EVENT_DATE AS FIRST_LOGIN FROM ( SELECT PLAYER_ID,EVENT_DATE, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY PLAYER_ID ORDER BY EVENT_DATE ASC) AS RK FROM ACTIVITY ) A WHERE A.RK=1
WITH A AS (SELECT PLAYER_ID,EVENT_DATE, ROW_NUMBER() OVER( PARTITION BY PLAYER_ID ORDER BY EVENT_DATE) RN FROM ACTIVITY) SELECT PLAYER_ID,EVENT_DATE FIRST_LOGIN FROM A WHERE RN=1
SELECT A.PLAYER_ID,A.EVENT_DATE AS FIRST_LOGIN FROM (SELECT PLAYER_ID,EVENT_DATE, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY PLAYER_ID ORDER BY EVENT_DATE) AS ROW_NUM FROM ACTIVITY )A WHERE A.ROW_NUM = 1
WITH CTE AS ( SELECT *, ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY PLAYER_ID ORDER BY EVENT_DATE ASC) AS RK FROM ACTIVITY ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, EVENT_DATE AS FIRST_LOGIN FROM CTE WHERE RK = 1
WITH CTE AS (SELECT PLAYER_ID,EVENT_DATE,DENSE_RANK() OVER(PARTITION BY PLAYER_ID ORDER BY EVENT_DATE) AS DR FROM ACTIVITY) SELECT PLAYER_ID,EVENT_DATE AS FIRST_LOGIN FROM CTE WHERE DR=1
